snippet.title: Parcel Simulator Steam Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Inspect and dissect parcels and packages in this parcel inspection simulator! Parcel Simulator is coming in 2023 and can now be wishlisted on Steam!

https://store.steampowered.com/app/2424010/Parcel_Simulator/

Join the Discord: https://discord.gg/W2xDCRhQha
Follow us on Twitter: https://twitter.com/parcelsim
Wishlist the game on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2424010/Parcel_Simulator/

#indiegame #indiedev #gaming
